<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA63">
<l>piṉ turakkuṅ kāṟṟiḻanta cūṟkoṇṭal pērntum pōy</l>
<l>vaṉṟiraikkaṇ vantaṇainta vāymaittē yaṉṟu</l>
<l>tirucceyya nēmiyāṉ ṟīyarakki mūkkum</l>
<l>parucceviyu mīrnta paraṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Turning back the cloud, with pregancy lost by the wind that drives it from behind,</l>
<l>has its true form that comes close into the strong waves in the Highest one</l>
<l>who that day sawed off the nose and big ears of the evil Rakṣasi</l>
<l>with [his] sacred just discus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
